imdb.plot outline: Taiwan is a high tech factory for the world's products. From the F1 of solar race-cars to the world's first and only transparent smartphone, we embark on a journey to the cutting edge of technology, to meet the innovators who are bringing tomorrow's products to life today.
imdb.title: Taiwan Revealed 2013: Innovation Island
